Package: politeness
Type: Package
Title: Detecting Politeness Features in Text
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Mike Yeomans, Alejandro Kantor, Dustin Tingley
Maintainer: Mike Yeomans <yeomans@fas.harvard.edu>
Description: Detecting linguistic markers of politeness in natural language.
    This package allows researchers to visualize and quantify politeness 
    differences between groups of documents.
    
    We thank the Spencer Foundation, the Hewlett Foundation, and
    Harvard's Institute for Quantitative Social Science for support.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    tm,
    quanteda,
    ggplot2,
    parallel,
    spacyr,
    textir,
    glmnet,
    ROCR,
    data.table,
    stringr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
